dct_description_sm: Freytag-Berndt und Artaria. Alternate title: Gesamtplan von Graz. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. In upper left margin: Freytag-Berndt Stadtplan. In lower left margin: "Herausengeben unter Mitwirkung der Vermessungsabteilung des Magistrates der Stadt Graz." In lower left corner: 626-1966. Accompanied by Guide ([12] p. Map Library does not have this guide.
